2. Government Order No. ASAP-1222 / P.No.110 / Ka. 14, D. 23.02.2023.
Reference No. 1 by order of Smt. Shital Sachin Nikam, Under Secretary, Registrar & Assistant, Regional Institute of Agricultural Extension Management Training (RAMETI), Pune.

Under the order, Ms. Nikam's deputation to the post was extended by 1 year.
The duration of this extension is. Ending on 31.03.2024.
